def mangle(text: str) -> str:
    upper = text.upper()
    remove_third = upper[:3] + upper[4:]
    last_third = remove_third[:-3] + remove_third[-2:]
    return last_third

    # Test cases

    print(mangle("hellothere"))
    print(mangle("42 degrees Celsius"))
